OL,3,CTwo men arrested over Golders Green
OL,4,Carson attack released on bail, police
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FTwo men who were arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with the arson attack on
OL,9,FJewish community ambulances in Golders
OL,10,FGreen have been released on bail,
OL,11,Fpolice said.
OL,13,FThe men ` aged 47 and 45, and of
OL,14,FBritish nationality ` were detained on
OL,15,FWednesday on suspicion of arson with
OL,16,Fintent to endanger life.
OL,18,FThey have been bailed until April
OL,19,Fwhile the investigation continues, the
OL,20,FMetropolitan Police said.
