OL,12,FChief Rabbi Ephraim Mirvis described
OL,13,Fthe attack, which took place in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of Monday, as
OL,15,F"particularly sickening".
OL,17,FHe told ITV News: "To attack
OL,18,Fambulances which exist for the sake of
OL,19,Fhelping people to be well and
OL,20,Fpreserving life.
