OL,3,CTwo men arrested over Golders Green
OL,4,Carson attack released on bail, police
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Here we are seeing displayed before
OL,8,Four eyes the forces of those who seek
OL,9,Fto destroy life as opposed to those
OL,10,Fwho are here to protect life."
OL,12,FHatzola is a non-profit, volunteer
OL,13,Forganisation that provides hospital
OL,14,Ftransportation and emergency care to
OL,15,Fthe local community, regardless of
OL,16,Freligion.
OL,18,FThe Met said searches had been carried
OL,19,Fout at addresses in the Kilburn and
OL,20,FKings Cross areas of London, where the
OL,21,Fmen had been arrested.
