OL,3,CTwo men arrested over Golders Green
OL,4,Carson attack released on bail, police
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FFurther searches have also taken place
OL,8,Fat two other addresses in north-west
OL,9,FLondon, the Met added.
OL,11,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,12,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,13,Fwhich is leading the investigation,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Although the two men have been
OL,15,Freleased from police custody, there
OL,16,Fare strict bail conditions in place
OL,17,Fwhile we continue to investigate their
OL,18,Fsuspected involvement in this incident.
