OL,3,CTwo men arrested over Golders Green
OL,4,Carson attack released on bail, police
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"I can reassure the public that we
OL,8,Fwill be closely monitoring these while
OL,9,Fwe carry out further inquiries.
OL,11,F"We continue to work to try and
OL,12,Fidentify all of those involved in this
OL,13,Fappalling attack and the investigation
OL,14,Fteam is working around the clock to do
OL,15,Fthis.
