OL,3,CTwo men arrested over Golders Green
OL,4,Carson attack released on bail, police
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"I'd like to thank the public and
OL,8,Fparticularly the local Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity in the area for their
OL,10,Fcontinued support and reiterate our
OL,11,Fappeal to anyone who might have
OL,12,Finformation that could assist with the
OL,13,Finvestigation to get in touch with us."
